                        "name": "brandonsavage",
                        "displayName": "Brandon Savage",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "According to the Wikipedia article on ISO 8601, the truncated UTC offset is valid. (See http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/ISO_8601#Time_zone_designators for more)\r\n\r\nThe fractional time is not ISO 8601; however, the removal of this does not affect the bug.",
